  * debian/patches/linuxefi_fix_relocate_coff.patch: fix typo in
    relocate_coff() causing issues with relocation of code in chainload.
    (LP: #1792575)

 -- Mathieu Trudel-Lapierre <cyphermox@ubuntu.com>  Mon, 17 Sep 2018 07:45:49 -0400

