grub2 (1.98~20091229-1) unstable; urgency=high

  * New Bazaar snapshot.
    - Fix slowness when $prefix uses an UUID.
      (Closes: #541145, LP: #420933)
    - Correctly set TARGET_CFLAGS. (Closes: #562953)

